data.description: Turnkey Furnished and move-in ready. Meticulously maintained home located in North Port with Ring doorbells/monitoring both front and back. Wired with ADT security system. This home is light bright, and features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 2 car garage and Hurricane Shutters. The galley style kitchen features plant shelves, stainless appliances, and a new disposal.  Enjoy the brand-new washer/dryer, fire alarms, living room and dining room flooring, ceiling fans, 3 yr old HVAC system, and 72" TV! Large 20'x20' living room with cathedral ceilings is open to the kitchen for easy living and entertaining. Ceiling fans in all rooms. Large master bedroom with a walk-in closet in addition to a second closet and en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower. A second bedroom with a large walk in closet and new carpet. Tile and carpeting in the 2nd/3rd bedrooms. Full hurricane shutters included, septic system just serviced. A very private fenced back yard. Nice appliances with a refrigerator with icemaker, new airfryer, r/o system, plenty of cabinet, counter and closet space.  The new shed with electric wired but is not attached to the house electricity, but it does have a drive-up ramp, side door, and workshop with tones of storage in addition to the 2 car garage.  The new fencing has a large swing out gate to enable you to bring in all your toys!
